00:09:31.176 --> 00:09:33.219
-Right?
-At my daughter's party,

00:09:33.303 --> 00:09:35.054
-Myung-heon was…
-You're so lucky, Myung-heon.

00:09:35.138 --> 00:09:37.140
I'd never won anything like that before.

00:09:37.682 --> 00:09:39.267
He even danced.

00:09:42.729 --> 00:09:43.938
That's hilarious.

00:09:58.953 --> 00:09:59.829
Mr. Kim.

00:09:59.913 --> 00:10:01.164
-Hi.
-Hello.

00:10:01.247 --> 00:10:02.540
-Hello.
-Hello.

00:10:03.499 --> 00:10:05.460
Okay, then.

