Looks like Team 2 all came in early today.

00:10:10.882 --> 00:10:13.426
Yes, we came in an hour early
and held a morning get-together.

00:10:13.509 --> 00:10:14.928
It was more of a breakfast meeting.

00:10:15.011 --> 00:10:16.930
The place we went to today was amazing.

00:10:17.013 --> 00:10:18.014
Was it?

00:10:18.097 --> 00:10:19.599
SALES TEAM 2 GENERAL MANAGER
DO JIN-WOO

00:10:19.682 --> 00:10:22.268
Your team seems to do
a lot of fun activities.

00:10:22.352 --> 00:10:23.269
Let's go.

00:10:23.353 --> 00:10:25.313
Is Mr. Baek in his office already?

00:10:25.396 --> 00:10:27.232
-We should say hello--
-That's…

00:10:27.315 --> 00:10:29.484
He told me he had some instructions
for me this morning,

00:10:29.567 --> 00:10:30.777
-so I--
-I'll just say hi.

00:10:30.860 --> 00:10:33.279
He seems very tired. Let's go.

00:10:33.363 --> 00:10:34.572
We should quickly say hello--

00:10:34.656 --> 00:10:36.824
-Let's go.
-Hang on.

00:10:37.533 --> 00:10:39.035
He's not there.

00:10:39.118 --> 00:10:40.870
-He's not?
-No. I was just looking around.

00:10:40.954 --> 00:10:43.081
-Looking around?
-Yes, around Mr. Baek's office.

00:10:43.164 --> 00:10:44.666
What?

00:10:45.792 --> 00:10:47.543
Mr. Baek and I are close enough.

00:10:48.920 --> 00:10:50.213
I'm sure.

00:10:50.296 --> 00:10:51.589
Move. What are you all doing?

00:10:54.175 --> 00:10:55.134
Jeez.

00:11:00.139 --> 00:11:01.391
What was that?

00:11:02.016 --> 00:11:03.518
-Are you okay?
-Mr. Kim!

00:11:03.601 --> 00:11:05.561
-Mr. Kim!
-Are you okay? I'm so sorry.

00:11:05.645 --> 00:11:07.146
Oh my gosh.

00:11:07.230 --> 00:11:09.065
-Are you okay, Mr. Kim?
-Goodness.

00:11:09.148 --> 00:11:11.651
-You don't seem okay.
-I'm okay. Jeez.

00:11:12.193 --> 00:11:13.611
I'm fine.

00:11:14.279 --> 00:11:15.780
I think you broke something.

00:11:15.863 --> 00:11:17.115
I heard a crack.

