In the year 2033,

00:21:46.201 --> 00:21:48.871
if Mr. Kim, a 51-year-old general manager
at a major company in Seoul,

00:21:48.954 --> 00:21:51.749
were to live to 100,
fortunately or unfortunately,

00:21:51.832 --> 00:21:54.668
how much would his family of three need?

00:21:54.752 --> 00:21:55.836
650 million won.

