for your transfers
in the second half of the year.

00:31:18.690 --> 00:31:20.609
-Mr. Heo Tae-hwan.
-Yes.

00:31:20.692 --> 00:31:23.195
Demonstrate
the confined space entry procedure.

00:31:23.695 --> 00:31:24.696
Sorry?

00:31:25.989 --> 00:31:27.032
Climb down.

